title: Dagmar Sirotkova - Zdrava vyziva Slunecnice
description: Vegetarian and vegan food, including vegan sandwiches, cookies, pies, salt croissants (usually on Wed), some gluten-free, macrobiotic food, and whole-grain pastry from a small private bakehouse as well. Shop is located under Vysehrad, a popular touristic destination, 2 tram stops from Charles Square.
